	<key>readme</key>
	<string># Password Generator

Generate passwords with customizable length and character set.

## Usage

* passgen [length] [pattern]              — basic (default: 18 chars, A-Za-z0-9)
* passgen panc [length] [pattern]         — with punctuation (!@#^&amp;*)
* passgen split [length] [by] [pattern]   — split by groups (default: 18/6)
* passgen panc split [length] [by] [pattern] — split with punctuation

Press Enter to copy the selected password to the clipboard.

## Pattern syntax

Characters can be listed directly (e.g. ABCabc012) or as ranges (e.g. A-Za-z0-9).
Punctuation range: !-* expands to !@#^&amp;*</string>
